&lt;li&gt;Design PLC hardware setups and topologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform risk analyses and design safety-critical electrical systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commission control systems of new ground systems and tweak to operator’s needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and support ground systems in all phases of their lifecycle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot PLC systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
