&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;A degree in electrical engineering, automation technology, or the like/ A certified engineer (German: ‘staatlich geprüfter Techniker’) in automation technology &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;2+ years of experience in automation and PLC technology, ideally using Beckhoff PLCs &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
