&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Knowledge about industrial fieldbus systems &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Basic understanding of electrical schematics &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Highly organized and proactive with high attention to detail &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Can-do attitude and outstanding communication skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Fluent in English&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
