&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Mission Brief&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Your main objective will be to work hands-on with our Data Platform, which consolidates all structured and unstructured&amp;nbsp;test, flight, and process data from across the company. Your work will empower data-driven decisions in various departments and enable us to generate valuable insights from cross-departmental data.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;More specifically, you will:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;40&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Build modern, scalable, and high-performance solutions for our&amp;nbsp;engineering&amp;nbsp;data platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;40&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Develop and deploy efficient ETL/ELT processes to ingest, transform, and load a large amount of data from diverse sources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;40&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Contribute to data modeling and architecture decisions to ensure consistency, availability, low latency, and long-term maintainability of the data landscape.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;40&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Ensure data quality through validation processes and adherence to data governance policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;40&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mission Brief&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Director of Production Engineering, you are accountable for the end-to-end production engineering capability across all manufacturing operations. Your mission is to industrialize development outputs into repeatable, scalable, and compliant serial production, ensuring manufacturing readiness, process stability, quality, cost efficiency, and on-time delivery. You lead the team that converts early procedures into robust production standards, embeds them in PLM/MES systems, and drives continuous improvement across the factory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You act as the primary interface between Engineering (design &amp;amp; development) and Manufacturing (production &amp;amp; operations)—ensuring requirements, procedures, tooling, documentation, test strategies, and digital manufacturing infrastructure are aligned for high-rate, high-quality execution.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your Role in Our Space Mission:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1) Production engineering strategy &amp;amp; leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and execute the production engineering roadmap, including industrialization strategy, standardization, and scalability for serial production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and develop a team of production/process/manufacturing engineers; set goals, coaching plans, hiring needs, and performance standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish clear governance for process ownership, engineering change implementation, and cross-functional decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2) Assembly, integration &amp;amp; test (AIT) process ownership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own manufacturing process definition across:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assembly: mechanical/electrical build procedures, torque specs, critical process parameters, work instructions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integration: subsystem integration strategy (e.g., avionics, propulsion, communications), sequencing, interfaces, and acceptance criteria.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Testing: functional, subsystem, and system-level test strategy; test readiness, execution plans, and troubleshooting methodology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure processes are repeatable, auditable, and optimized for safety, throughput, and quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3) Industrialization &amp;amp; manufacturing readiness (NPI / transfer to production)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with development teams to receive initial procedures and convert them into production-ready standards (control plans, critical-to-quality characteristics where relevant).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive manufacturing readiness reviews, line readiness, and process qualification for new products, variants, or upgrades.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the “first builds”/pilot runs, capturing learnings and stabilizing procedures for volume execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4) Digital manufacturing (PLM/MES) &amp;amp; configuration control&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the production engineering contribution to PLM/MES:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate procedures into structured digital work instructions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure traceability, configuration control, and alignment of as-built data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee creation and maintenance of:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;mBOM (Manufacturing Bill of Materials)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BOP (Bill of Process)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Routings, work centers, and data collection points for quality and traceability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure engineering changes are implemented cleanly and quickly, with minimal disruption to production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5) Documentation, compliance &amp;amp; quality partnership&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure comp

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Mission Brief&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun CommentStart CommentHighlightPipeRest CommentHighlightRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot;&gt;You will help us build and maintain all kinds of different test-benches and test-sites but also our launchpad in Andoya for our launcher &quot;Spectrum&quot;. Besides planning the systems with our ECAD program “WSCAD”, your tasks include carrying out the build-up, maintenance, troubleshooting, implementing upgrades and more. Some hands-on work will be part of your daily business as well. You will have close exchange with our engineering departments across all our different testing and launch sites! You use your expertise to guide and manage the electrical aspects of medium-sized projects, including overseeing small electrical teams and coordinating with external companies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun CommentStart CommentHighlightPipeRest CommentHighlightRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot;&gt;Your Role in Our Space Mission&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun CommentHighlightRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;EOP CommentHighlightPipeRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the electrical aspects of medium-sized projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate work in small workgroups and coordinate external companies and suppliers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan electric systems for various in-house test benches (24VDC &amp;amp; 230/400VAC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create circuit diagrams for control cabinets acc. to local and company standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wire different kinds of sensors and actors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Construct and wire control cabinets and whole electrical systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install control cabinets and other electrical systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshooting of complex electrical systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Carry-out standardized functional testing of control cabinets and preparation of measurement protocols&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;EOP CommentHighlightPipeRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;Qualification Checklist&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;You have a completed apprenticeship as electrician, and a further education &quot;staatl. gepr. Techniker&quot;, &quot;Meister&quot; or similar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;You should have planned and worked with industrial electrical systems (24V, 230/400V) for at least 5 years&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;You have extensive general knowledge of electrical systems and components, including industrial sensors and actuators &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;You have experience with ECAD programs (Preferably WSCAD)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;You are experienced with applicable electrics standards and norms (VDE/EN)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;You have a high reliability and sense of responsibility&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;s

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Mission Brief&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be an integral part of the Avionics, Guidance, Navigation &amp;amp; Control (AGNC) department, specifically the Harness &amp;amp; Structures team, that designs the complete Launch Vehicle harness in close collaboration with the in-house harnessing production team as well as all relevant stakeholders from other departments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be the product owner of the Launch Vehicle Harnesses belonging to the next generation of our Launcher. You will own the lifecycle of it, manage associated interfaces and ensure delivery on time, budget and scope. Interdisciplinary tasks and fast paced R&amp;amp;D are your daily business, and you thrive in that kind of environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun CommentStart CommentHighlightPipeRest CommentHighlightRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot;&gt;Your Role in Our Space Mission&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;EOP CommentHighlightPipeRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Carry out the electrical design of harnesses. Starting from the harness architecture through a complete electrical schematic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop the harness architecture according to the Launcher requirements and design guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the design and configuration of Launch Vehicle harnesses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interpret system-level diagrams to ensure harness compatibility across subsystems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engineer harnesses with attention to pinning, shielding, routing, and EMI/EMC compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate manufacturing files and documentation (e.g., BOMs, harness testing files, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track design changes and adapt harnesses accordingly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with stakeholders (structures, propulsion, sensor, actuator teams) to align interfaces and requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support integration and production activities, ensuring manufacturability and installation feasibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate in maintaining the sensor and actuator database up to date for harness integration consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;EOP CommentHighlightPipeRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;Qualification Checklist&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BSc/MSc in Electrical, Electronics, Aerospace Engineering, or related field&lt;/li&gt;
