&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;Mission Brief&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW163219142 BCX8&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW163219142 BCX8&quot;&gt;We’re building the future of aerospace—and safety is at the heart of our journey. As our local HSE Specialist, you’ll be a driving force behind our commitment to a safe, healthy, and sustainable workplace. Collaborate, innovate, and lead by example as we redefine what’s possible, together.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;EOP Selected SCXW163219142 BCX8&quot; data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun CommentStart CommentHighlightPipeRest CommentHighlightRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot;&gt;Your Role in Our Space Mission&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun CommentHighlightRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;EOP CommentHighlightPipeRest SCXW114497174 BCX8&quot; data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW158599622 BCX8&quot; data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW158599622 BCX8&quot;&gt;As a local HSE Specialist at Isar Aerospace, you play a central role in ensuring our workplace remains safe, healthy, and compliant. You will actively implement HSE policies, engage teams in safety initiatives, and drive continuous improvement to support our operational excellence and sustainability goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;EOP Selected SCXW158599622 BCX8&quot; data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233279&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Lead the implementation and monitoring of compliance with all local HSE regulations, company policies, and industry standards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Conduct and oversee regular site inspections, risk assessments, and incident investigations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Develop, deliver, and evaluate comprehensive HSE training and awareness programs for all staff&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Proactively identify, assess, and mitigate workplace hazards and environmental risks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to embed and promote a proactive safety culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233279&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:360}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Ensure the maintenance of accurate HSE records, reports, and documentation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Lead and coordinate emergency preparedness and response activities on site&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Drive and manage continuous improvement initiatives in safety and environmental performance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mission Brief&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of the internal logistics team, the primary purpose of the role is to ensure that the daily functions and procedures related to internal logistics in the manufacturing plant run smoothly and efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your Role in Our Space Mission:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform general warehouse activities: loading and unloading of goods, booking goods receipt, picking, storage and retrieval of goods, transfer of goods between different warehouses and to the different production process steps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure traceability of goods in the warehouse (correct labeling, storing, etc)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with the various departments involved in the management of internal logistics, such as purchasing and production, aligning the warehouse operations with the production needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Push optimisations regarding resources, processes and services to achieve the highest possible profit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Record all movements of goods within the warehouse&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the integrity and correct storage of goods in the warehouse (according to the requirements of temperature, humidity, weight, hazardousness...)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct regular inventory checks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Carry out the cutting process of raw materials after receipt and subsequent storage in the warehouse (putaway)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep the warehouse area clean and organized&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate forklifts to move products within the warehouse&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualification Checklist&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Completed training as a logistics specialist or lateral entry possible with IHK further training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3-5 years experience in logistics, warehouse management or similar areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relevant experience using Warehouse Management Systems&lt;/li&gt;
